      <div class="about-hero__inner">
        <h1 class="about-hero__title">So… who am I?</h1>

        <div class="about-hero__answer">
          <p>
            I’m Brandon Vélez Johnson, a language and Bible nerd, a mental
            health counselor, and someone who cares not just what the Bible
            says, but how it impacts people.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

